A simple translation activity that users Google's Translation service on the Web.  More than 150 language pairs are supported and the feature "random word" lets you learn new translations whenever you are bored.

Author: Cédric Beust (cedric@beust.com)

Note: this application reuses existing work by:
- Richard Midwinter, Emeric Vernat and Juan B Cabral (for the interface to the Google API)
- Alexander Day Chaffee and Gary Gregory (for a list of HTML entities).
- Flag icons from http://www.famfamfam.com

